 674:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_anim.c **** /**
 675:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_anim.c ****  * Called when an animation is completed to do the necessary things
 676:Drivers/lvgl/src/misc/lv_anim.c ****  * e.g. repeat, play in reverse, delete etc.
